export default function loginComponent() {
    return(
        <form class='login-container'>
            <label for="firstName">First Name </label>
            <input type="text" id="firstName" class='login-input' placeholder='John' />
            <label for="lastName">Last Name </label>
            <input type="text" id="lastName" class='login-input' placeholder='Doe' />
            <label for="dob">Date of Birth </label>
            <input type="date" id="dob" class='login-input' placeholder='1990-08-30' />
            <label for="email">Email </label>
            <input type="text" id="email" class='login-input' placeholder='john.doe@example.com' />
            <label for="address">Address </label>
            <input type="text" id="address" class='login-input' placeholder='789 Birch S' />
            <label for="password">Password </label>
            <input type="text" id="password" class='login-input' placeholder='****' />
            <label for="confirmPassword">Confirm Password </label>
            <input type="text" id="confirmPassword" class='login-input' placeholder='****' />
            <button type="submit" value="submit" />
        </form>
    );
}
